### JPA: 게시글 + 댓글 단건 조회 (Fetch Join)
GET http://localhost:18080/api/boards/1/with-comments

### JPA: 모든 게시글 + 댓글 - N+1 발생 (의도적)
GET http://localhost:18080/api/boards?lazy=true

### JPA: 모든 게시글 + 댓글 - Fetch Join으로 해결
GET http://localhost:18080/api/boards?fetch=join

### JPA: 게시글 등록
POST http://localhost:18080/api/boards
Content-Type: application/json

